column5: Do you really want to do this?  http://wimp.com/racetide/ <http://wimp.com/racetide/>
Great to see you keeping yourself occupied Albert... Billy Bob already posted it today!  Glad all went well today.... tomorrow will be a real special Sunday dinner.
I don't even like to go to the grocery store when it is going to be busy.
She'll still be there Albert.. don't you worry about that.. now get your friggin elbows off the table !!!!

Irish, I actually have knack in the kitchen and she would always remind me "did you wash your hands" if I had anything to do with dinner. I'd wash them if I had or not! I'll keep doing it,she may be looking!
